{{expand Italian| Accademia di belle arti di Foggia|date=September 2016}} 
The '''Accademia di Belle Arti di Foggia''' is an academy of fine arts located in [[Foggia]], Italy. It was founded in 1970.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Giovanna Cassese|title= Accademie Patrimoni di Belle Arti|publisher=Gangemi, 2013|isbn=8849276710}}</ref>

