'''Ars Fennica Award''' presented by the Henna and Pertti Niemistö Ars Fennica Art Foundation is the biggest [[Finland|Finnish]] [[art]] award that has been awarded since 1991. The Ars Fennica art award is made annually to one artist in recognition of distinctive artistic output of high merit. The award is 40,000 euros.<ref name=jeppe>{{cite web |url=http://yle.fi/uutiset/ars_fennica_-palkinto_tanskalaiselle_jeppe_heinille/6776278 |title=Ars Fennica -palkinto tanskalaiselle Jeppe Heinille |date=August 14, 2013 |website=yle.fi |publisher=Yle |language=Finnish |accessdate=14 May 2016}}</ref>
